    {
      "id": "el_8",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 535,
      "y": 125,
      "width": 297,
      "height": 234,
      "text": "Area = (1/2) × base × height\n\nHeron's: s=(a+b+c)/2\n  Area = √[s(s-a)(s-b)(s-c)]\n\nEquilateral (side a):\n  Area = (√3/4) × a²\n  Height = (√3/2) × a\n\nRight △: Area = (1/2) × leg₁ × leg₂\n\nWHY: Triangle = half of rectangle with\n  same base and height (b×h / 2).\n\nEx: b=10, h=6 → Area=1/2×10×6=30",
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 13,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "seed": 800,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 8,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "groupIds": [
        "f1"
      ],
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Area = (1/2) × base × height\n\nHeron's: s=(a+b+c)/2\n  Area = √[s(s-a)(s-b)(s-c)]\n\nEquilateral (side a):\n  Area = (√3/4) × a²\n  Height = (√3/2) × a\n\nRight △: Area = (1/2) × leg₁ × leg₂\n\nWHY: Triangle = half of rectangle with\n  same base and height (b×h / 2).\n\nEx: b=10, h=6 → Area=1/2×10×6=30",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "frameId": null,
      "roundness": null
