    {
      "id": "el_26",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 65,
      "y": 813,
      "width": 231,
      "height": 202,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: Area = 120×80 = 9600 m²\n  Peri = 2(120+80) = 400 m\nStep 2: Cost = 400×15 = Rs.6000\n\nTRICK:\nArea = L×B, Peri = 2(L+B)\nFencing = perimeter × rate\n\n  ┌──── 120 m ────┐\n  │               │ 80 m\n  └───────────────┘\n\nAnswer: Area=9600m², Peri=400m ✓",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 12,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
