    {
      "id": "el_31",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 535,
      "y": 813,
      "width": 260,
      "height": 202,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: a = √5625 = 75 m\nStep 2: P = 4×75 = 300 m\n  Cost = 300×12 = Rs.3600\n\nTRICK:\n√5625: ends in 5, try 75²\n75² = 5625 ✓ (use (a5)² = a(a+1)|25)\n\n  ┌──── 75 ────┐\n  │  A = 5625  │ 75\n  └────────────┘\n\nAnswer: Side=75m, P=300m ✓",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 12,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
