    {
      "id": "el_36",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1005,
      "y": 797,
      "width": 224,
      "height": 231,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: s = (13+14+15)/2 = 21\nStep 2: Area = √(21×8×7×6)\n  = √7056 = 84 cm²\n\nTRICK:\nHeron's: √(s(s-a)(s-b)(s-c))\n21×8=168, 7×6=42, 168×42=7056\n√7056 = 84 (memorize: 84²=7056)\n\n       /\\\n   15 /  \\ 13\n     /____\\\n       14\n\nAnswer: Area = 84 cm² ✓",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 12,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "seed": 3600,
      "version": 1,
