      ],
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: s = (13+14+15)/2 = 21\nStep 2: Area = √(21×8×7×6)\n  = √7056 = 84 cm²\n\nTRICK:\nHeron's: √(s(s-a)(s-b)(s-c))\n21×8=168, 7×6=42, 168×42=7056\n√7056 = 84 (memorize: 84²=7056)\n\n       /\\\n   15 /  \\ 13\n     /____\\\n       14\n\nAnswer: Area = 84 cm² ✓",
      "autoResize": true,
