    {
      "id": "el_41",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 65,
      "y": 1178,
      "width": 281,
      "height": 216,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: r = 14 cm\nStep 2: Area = πr²/2 = 22/7×196/2 = 308\n  Peri = πr+2r = 44+28 = 72\n\nTRICK:\nSemicircle peri = πr + 2r (NOT πr + d)\nInclude the flat diameter edge!\n\n     _________\n    /    |    \\\n   /     |r=14 \\\n  /______|______\\\n\nAnswer: Area=308cm², Peri=72cm ✓",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 12,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "seed": 4100,
