      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: r = 14 cm\nStep 2: Area = πr²/2 = 22/7×196/2 = 308\n  Peri = πr+2r = 44+28 = 72\n\nTRICK:\nSemicircle peri = πr + 2r (NOT πr + d)\nInclude the flat diameter edge!\n\n     _________\n    /    |    \\\n   /     |r=14 \\\n  /______|______\\\n\nAnswer: Area=308cm², Peri=72cm ✓",
