    {
      "id": "el_46",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 535,
      "y": 1194,
      "width": 303,
      "height": 202,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: a=25, b=15, h=12\nStep 2: A = (1/2)(a+b)×h\n  = (1/2)(40)×12 = 240\n\nTRICK:\nTrapezium = avg of parallel sides × height\n= (25+15)/2 × 12 = 20×12 = 240\n\n    ┌── 15 ──┐\n   /    12    \\\n  └──── 25 ───┘\n\nAnswer: Area = 240 cm² ✓",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 12,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
