      "originalText": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: a=25, b=15, h=12\nStep 2: A = (1/2)(a+b)×h\n  = (1/2)(40)×12 = 240\n\nTRICK:\nTrapezium = avg of parallel sides × height\n= (25+15)/2 × 12 = 20×12 = 240\n\n    ┌── 15 ──┐\n   /    12    \\\n  └──── 25 ───┘\n\nAnswer: Area = 240 cm² ✓",
