    {
      "id": "el_51",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1005,
      "y": 1194,
      "width": 224,
      "height": 245,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: R = 21+3.5 = 24.5m\nStep 2: Path = π(R²-r²)\n  = 22/7 × (600.25-441) = 500.5\n\nTRICK:\nUse: π(R+r)(R-r) = π×45.5×3.5\n= 22/7 × 159.25 = 500.5\nTRAP: π(R²-r²) ≠ π(R-r)²\n\n  ┌──────────────────┐\n  │  ╱ ○ R=24.5 ╲   │\n  │ │  ○ r=21    │  │ path=3.5\n  │  ╲          ╱   │\n  └──────────────────┘\n\nAnswer: Path area = 500.5 m² ✓",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 12,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "seed": 5100,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 51,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "groupIds": [
        "type_6"
      ],
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: R = 21+3.5 = 24.5m\nStep 2: Path = π(R²-r²)\n  = 22/7 × (600.25-441) = 500.5\n\nTRICK:\nUse: π(R+r)(R-r) = π×45.5×3.5\n= 22/7 × 159.25 = 500.5\nTRAP: π(R²-r²) ≠ π(R-r)²\n\n  ┌──────────────────┐\n  │  ╱ ○ R=24.5 ╲   │\n  │ │  ○ r=21    │  │ path=3.5\n  │  ╲          ╱   │\n  └──────────────────┘\n\nAnswer: Path area = 500.5 m² ✓",
