    {
      "id": "el_56",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 65,
      "y": 1589,
      "width": 238,
      "height": 274,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: Arc = (120/360)×2πr\n  = (1/3)×132 = 44 cm\nStep 2: Area = (120/360)×πr²\n  = (1/3)×1386 = 462 cm²\n\nTRICK:\nFraction = θ/360 (of full circle)\nArc = fraction × 2πr\nArea = fraction × πr²\nAlso: Area = (1/2)×arc×r\n\n      /|\n     / |\n  r / 120° r=21\n   /___|\n   arc=44\n\nAnswer: Arc=44cm, Area=462cm² ✓",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 12,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "seed": 5600,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 56,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "groupIds": [
        "type_7"
      ],
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: Arc = (120/360)×2πr\n  = (1/3)×132 = 44 cm\nStep 2: Area = (120/360)×πr²\n  = (1/3)×1386 = 462 cm²\n\nTRICK:\nFraction = θ/360 (of full circle)\nArc = fraction × 2πr\nArea = fraction × πr²\nAlso: Area = (1/2)×arc×r\n\n      /|\n     / |\n  r / 120° r=21\n   /___|\n   arc=44\n\nAnswer: Arc=44cm, Area=462cm² ✓",
