    {
      "id": "el_61",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 535,
      "y": 1589,
      "width": 274,
      "height": 245,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: Outer = (80+10)×(60+10) = 6300\n  Inner = 80×60 = 4800\nStep 2: Path = 6300-4800 = 1500\n\nTRICK:\nOuter path = 2w(L+B+2w)\n= 2×5×(80+60+10) = 1500\nInner path = 2w(L+B-2w)\n\n  ┌──── 90 ────┐\n  │ ┌── 80 ──┐ │ 70\n  │ │ PARK   │ │\n  │ └────────┘ │\n  └────────────┘\n\nAnswer: Path area = 1500 m² ✓",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 12,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
