    {
      "id": "el_66",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1005,
      "y": 1605,
      "width": 252,
      "height": 231,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: d²=L²+B² → 625=L²+49\nStep 2: L²=576 → L=24\n  Area = 24×7 = 168\n\nTRICK:\nPythagorean triplet: 7,24,25\nMemorize common triplets!\n3,4,5 | 5,12,13 | 7,24,25 | 8,15,17\n\n  ┌──── 24 ────┐\n  │    ╱  d=25 │ 7\n  └────────────┘\n  7² + 24² = 25² ✓\n\nAnswer: L=24cm, Area=168cm² ✓",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 12,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "seed": 6600,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 66,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1,
