        "type_9"
      ],
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: d²=L²+B² → 625=L²+49\nStep 2: L²=576 → L=24\n  Area = 24×7 = 168\n\nTRICK:\nPythagorean triplet: 7,24,25\nMemorize common triplets!\n3,4,5 | 5,12,13 | 7,24,25 | 8,15,17\n\n  ┌──── 24 ────┐\n  │    ╱  d=25 │ 7\n  └────────────┘\n  7² + 24² = 25² ✓\n\nAnswer: L=24cm, Area=168cm² ✓",
