    {
      "id": "el_86",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 65,
      "y": 2426,
      "width": 274,
      "height": 245,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: Wire = 2πr = 132 cm\nStep 2: Side = 132/4 = 33 cm\n  Circle = 1386, Square = 1089\n  Diff = 297 cm²\n\nTRICK:\nSame perimeter: circle > square (area)\nRatio ≈ 14:11\nCircle always wins for max area!\n\n  ○ r=21 ───bent──> □ s=33\n  P=132            P=132\n  A=1386           A=1089\n  Diff = 297\n\nAnswer: Diff = 297 cm² ✓",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 12,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "seed": 8600,
      "version": 1,
