      "originalText": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: Wire = 2πr = 132 cm\nStep 2: Side = 132/4 = 33 cm\n  Circle = 1386, Square = 1089\n  Diff = 297 cm²\n\nTRICK:\nSame perimeter: circle > square (area)\nRatio ≈ 14:11\nCircle always wins for max area!\n\n  ○ r=21 ───bent──> □ s=33\n  P=132            P=132\n  A=1386           A=1089\n  Diff = 297\n\nAnswer: Diff = 297 cm² ✓",
