    {
      "id": "el_91",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 535,
      "y": 2410,
      "width": 216,
      "height": 216,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: P=100, L+B=50\nStep 2: Max when L=B (SQUARE!)\n  L=B=25, Area=625\n\nTRICK:\nMax rectangle area = (P/4)²\n= (100/4)² = 25² = 625\nCircle max: P²/(4π) ≈ 795.8\n\n  ┌──── 25 ────┐\n  │  Max Area  │ 25\n  └────────────┘\n\nAnswer: Max Area = 625 m² ✓",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 12,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "seed": 9100,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 91,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1,
