      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: P=100, L+B=50\nStep 2: Max when L=B (SQUARE!)\n  L=B=25, Area=625\n\nTRICK:\nMax rectangle area = (P/4)²\n= (100/4)² = 25² = 625\nCircle max: P²/(4π) ≈ 795.8\n\n  ┌──── 25 ────┐\n  │  Max Area  │ 25\n  └────────────┘\n\nAnswer: Max Area = 625 m² ✓",
      "autoResize": true,
