      "originalText": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: Room=120m², Tile=0.25m²\nStep 2: Tiles = 120/0.25 = 480\n  Cost = 480×25 = Rs.12000\n\nTRICK:\nCount tiles per side:\n15/0.5 × 8/0.5 = 30×16 = 480\n(convert units first!)\n\n  ┌──── 15m ────┐\n  │ □□□□□□...   │ 8m\n  │ 30 × 16     │\n  └─────────────┘\n  Tile=0.5m → 480 tiles\n\nAnswer: 480 tiles, Rs.12000 ✓",
