    {
      "id": "el_101",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 65,
      "y": 2837,
      "width": 252,
      "height": 288,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: Square = 14² = 196\n  4 quadrants = πr² = 22/7×49 = 154\nStep 2: Shaded = 196-154 = 42\n\nTRICK:\nShaded = total - unshaded\n4 quadrants (r=7) = 1 full circle\n= π×7² = 154\n196-154 = 42\n\n  ┌──────────────┐\n  │╲  shaded   ╱ │ s=14\n  │  ╲       ╱   │\n  │   (○○○○)     │ 4 quadrants\n  │  ╱       ╲   │ r=7 each\n  │╱  shaded   ╲ │\n  └──────────────┘\n\nAnswer: Shaded = 42 cm² ✓",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 12,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "seed": 10100,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 101,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
