      "locked": false,
      "groupIds": [
        "type_16"
      ],
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: Square = 14² = 196\n  4 quadrants = πr² = 22/7×49 = 154\nStep 2: Shaded = 196-154 = 42\n\nTRICK:\nShaded = total - unshaded\n4 quadrants (r=7) = 1 full circle\n= π×7² = 154\n196-154 = 42\n\n  ┌──────────────┐\n  │╲  shaded   ╱ │ s=14\n  │  ╲       ╱   │\n  │   (○○○○)     │ 4 quadrants\n  │  ╱       ╲   │ r=7 each\n  │╱  shaded   ╲ │\n  └──────────────┘\n\nAnswer: Shaded = 42 cm² ✓",
